        "text": [
          "۳۳۵. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام): لِكُلِّ امْرِئٍ فِى مَالِهِ شَرِيكَانِ، الْوَارِثُ وَالْحَوَادِثُ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
            "335. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: There are two sharers in the property of every person — successors and accidents."
